case 1164: //Varock c.triggerTele(3213+misc.random(1),3424+misc.random(1), 0); break; case 1167: //Lumbridge c.triggerTele(3222+misc.random(1),3218+misc.random(1), 0); break; case 1170: //Falador c.triggerTele(2965+misc.random(1),3380+misc.random(1), 0); break;
